statements: SELECT * FROM seed_distribution;
SELECT id, seed_name, farmer_id FROM seed_distribution;
SELECT seed_name, distribution_date FROM seed_distribution WHERE crop_performance = 'good';
SELECT * FROM seed_distribution WHERE distribution_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT id, seed_name, farmer_id, crop_performance FROM seed_distribution ORDER BY distribution_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM seed_distribution WHERE farmer_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000'
SELECT seed_name, distribution_date, crop_performance FROM seed_distribution WHERE distribution_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY distribution_date DESC
SELECT * FROM seed_distribution WHERE seed_name = 'Corn' AND crop_performance = 'High'
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT farmer_id) FROM seed_distribution WHERE distribution_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31'
SELECT seed_name, COUNT(*) AS total_distributions FROM seed_distribution GROUP BY seed_name HAVING total_distributions > 5 ORDER BY total_distributions DESC
SELECT * FROM Distribution
SELECT distributor_name, distributor_location FROM Distribution ORDER BY distributor_name DESC
SELECT seed_type, COUNT(*) AS num_distributions FROM Distribution GROUP BY seed_type
SELECT * FROM CropPerformance WHERE crop_yield > 10000
SELECT farmer_name, crop_type FROM CropPerformance WHERE crop_health='Excellent'
SELECT * FROM Distribution WHERE seed_type = 'Corn' ORDER BY distribution_date DESC;
SELECT distributor_id, distributor_name, distributor_location FROM Distribution WHERE distributor_location LIKE '%City%' ORDER BY distributor_name;
SELECT distributor_name, seed_type, distribution_date FROM Distribution JOIN CropPerformance ON distributor_id = farmer_id WHERE crop_yield > 100 ORDER BY distribution_date ASC;

SELECT d.distributor_name, d.distributor_location, c.crop_health FROM Distribution d JOIN CropPerformance c ON d.distributor_id = c.farmer_id WHERE d.seed_type = 'Wheat' AND c.crop_health = 'Good' ORDER BY d.distributor_name, c.crop_health;

SELECT c.farmer_name, c.crop_type, d.distributor_location FROM CropPerformance c JOIN Distribution d ON c.farmer_id = d.distributor_id WHERE d.distribution_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' ORDER BY c.farmer_name DESC, d.distributor_location;
SELECT * FROM Farmers;
SELECT farmer_name, location FROM Farmers ORDER BY location DESC;
SELECT seed_name, quantity FROM Seeds WHERE quantity > 100;
SELECT seed_name, yield, quality_rating FROM Seeds s JOIN CropPerformance cp ON s.seed_id = cp.seed_id;
SELECT farmer_name, yield FROM Farmers f JOIN CropPerformance cp ON f.farmer_id = cp.farmer_id ORDER BY yield ASC;
SELECT * FROM Farmers WHERE location = 'California';
SELECT farmer_name, location FROM Farmers ORDER BY farmer_name ASC;
SELECT seed_name, quantity FROM Seeds WHERE quantity > 100 ORDER BY quantity DESC;
SELECT f.farmer_name, s.seed_name, cp.yield FROM Farmers f JOIN CropPerformance cp ON f.farmer_id = cp.farmer_id JOIN Seeds s ON cp.seed_id = s.seed_id WHERE cp.yield > 500 ORDER BY cp.yield DESC;

SELECT f.farmer_name, cp.yield, cp.quality_rating FROM Farmers f LEFT JOIN CropPerformance cp ON f.farmer_id = cp.farmer_id WHERE cp.quality_rating >= 4.0 ORDER BY cp.quality_rating DESC, cp.yield ASC;
SELECT * FROM farmers
SELECT farmer_id, farmer_name FROM farmers
SELECT location, crop_type FROM farmers WHERE farmer_id = 1
SELECT seed_name, supplier, expiration_date FROM seeds ORDER BY expiration_date DESC
SELECT farmer_name, year, crop_yield FROM crop_performance WHERE crop_yield > 500
SELECT farmer_name, crop_type, location FROM farmers ORDER BY location DESC, crop_type ASC
SELECT DISTINCT seed_type, supplier FROM seeds WHERE expiration_date > '2023-01-01'
SELECT farmer_name, crop_yield, year FROM farmers JOIN crop_performance ON farmers.farmer_id = crop_performance.farmer_id WHERE crop_yield > 500 ORDER BY year DESC
SELECT seed_name, expiration_date FROM seeds WHERE supplier = 'ABC Seeds' AND seed_type = 'Corn' ORDER BY expiration_date ASC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT farmer_id) AS total_farmers, AVG(quantity) AS average_quantity FROM distribution GROUP BY seed_id HAVING total_farmers > 10 AND average_quantity < 1000
SELECT * FROM farmers;
SELECT farmer_name, farmer_location FROM farmers ORDER BY farmer_location DESC;
SELECT seed_name, seed_description FROM seeds WHERE seed_id = 3;
SELECT farmer_name, farmer_location FROM farmers WHERE farmer_location = 'California';
SELECT * FROM distribution WHERE quantity > 100 ORDER BY distribution_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM farmers;
SELECT farmer_name, farmer_location FROM farmers ORDER BY farmer_name DESC;
SELECT seed_name, seed_description FROM seeds WHERE seed_id = 3;
SELECT farmer_name, seed_name, distribution_date FROM farmers JOIN distribution ON farmers.farmer_id = distribution.farmer_id ORDER BY distribution_date ASC;

SELECT farmer_name, crop_yield, disease_occurrence FROM farmers JOIN distribution ON farmers.farmer_id = distribution.farmer_id JOIN crop_performance ON distribution.distribution_id = crop_performance.distribution_id WHERE disease_occurrence = TRUE;
